障。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n脫支大行動<br />\n<br />\nPostal code 就打000000<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NALhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=4963897d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"f928966d9eaa09e73f98818e02fd538c84755cfc","tid":1488580,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fedcee221f2377e9ec1aacdbd5175d194a5ab3b","tid":1488580,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:21:22.000Z","msg":"57358 signed."},{"pid":"53d0e938c0e40c0c5d2e32799ff0d73ebd7fddf1","tid":1488580,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:42:46.000Z","msg":"57,400 signed"},{"pid":"6f5b57a95bc9d68c111355dc38e56e638400c4d2","tid":1488580,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"提升bno國際認受性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國護照去美國永遠都要簽證<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nttps://<a href=\"http://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/visa-waiver-program-vwp-should-be-given-british-national-overseas-passport-holder\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fvisa-waiver-program-vwp-should-be-given-british-national-overseas-passport-holder&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NALhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=da05f132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">petitions.whitehouse.gov